{"id": 57607, "date": "2025-07-06T04:00:03", "date_gmt": "2025-07-06T11:00:03", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57607"}, "modified": "2026-03-02T15:12:42", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-02T23:12:42", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-6-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/06/kingdom-of-days-july-6-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 6"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1968:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles play a gig at Le Teendezvous in New Shrewsbury, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"2948\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1968-0706/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0706.jpg?fit=294%2C413&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"294,413\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1968-0706\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0706.jpg?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0706.jpg?fit=294%2C413&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2948 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0706.jpg?resize=294%2C413&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"294\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0706.jpg?w=294&amp;ssl=1 294w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0706.jpg?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 294px) 100vw, 294px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band headline two shows at The Main Point in Bryn Mawr, Pennsylvania.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band work on &#8220;Backstreets&#8221; at a\u00a0<em>Born to Run\u00a0</em>recording session at the Record Plant in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Gary Busey and The Old Dog Band on stage for &#8220;Carol&#8221; at the Sundance Saloon in Calabasas, California.</p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the boys play their fourth of six nights at the Brendan Byrne Arena&#8217;s opening stand. Recordings of &#8220;Independence Day,&#8221; &#8220;Cadillac Ranch,&#8221; and &#8220;Racing in the Street&#8221; will eventually be released on <em>Live 1975-85</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GSPNMNO5Enc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hcZFiBWrK4c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dCILTxWFsow?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Night Two in Cincinnati on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour. Listen in on the soundcheck below, including a never-played &#8220;The Good, The Bad, and The Ugly.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-mB3khd4m-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/mB3khd4m?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band close out their Wembley Stadium stand with their third of three nights in London. Steve Van Zandt makes his third consecutive encore appearance. Also in attendance tonight: Phil Collins, Mark Knopfler, Roger Taylor, and John Entwhistle.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2Epn-TJSqIM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;start=135&#038;wmo