://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2019-07-06a.jpg?resize=199%2C300&amp;ssl=1 199w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 636px) 100vw, 636px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19446\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2019-07-06b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2019-07-06b.jpg?fit=1255%2C830&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1255,830\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593030392&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2019-07-06b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2019-07-06b.jpg?fit=300%2C198&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2019-07-06b.jpg?fit=758%2C501&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19446 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2019-07-06b.jpg?resize=758%2C501&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"501\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2019-07-06b.jpg?w=1255&amp;ssl=1 1255w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2019-07-06b.jpg?resize=300%2C198&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2019-07-06b.jpg?resize=1024%2C677&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2019-07-06b.jpg?resize=768%2C508&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2021:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its limited return engagement at the St. James Theater in New York City. In attendance tonight: Dave Marsh and Barbara Carr.</p>\n<p><strong>2023:\u00a0</strong>Peter Gabriel, Billy Joel, and Jon Bon Jovi are among the fans in attendance at Hyde Park, where Bruce and the E Street Band play their first of two shows on their 2023 World Tour.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/qs_vbgeV2-Q?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PeAhFEkCGfA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Bruce wraps up one Wembley stand, kicks off another, records performances for Live 1975-85, and more. Plus: Listen to a 1984 soundcheck that includes a never-played &#8220;The Good, The Bad, and The Ugly.&#8221;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 52338, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_m